{"tid":967134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在唐人街性侵90多歲老婦　警公布長相後遭逮","createTime":"2019-01-03T09:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T13:29:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d43f56268e3aa8c72602af70fad7267327edcf66","tid":967134,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190103/640_5e7d531f018b572881b1eea021d5f1af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190103%2F640_5e7d531f018b572881b1eea021d5f1af.jpg&h=67f40e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《KTVU》報導，舊金山女警葛瑞絲（Grace Gatpandan）指出，一名男子被控於12月31日下午，在唐人街對90多歲女性性侵，並於1月1日下午4點左右被逮。<br />\n<br />\n該起事件發生在除夕下午12點36分左右，嫌疑人年紀約為35到40歲，身高約為斯托克頓街約為5英尺11英寸到6英尺(180公分到182公分)，體重約為180磅(約81.6公斤)，身穿淺灰色連帽運動服、藍色背心，黑色條紋褲子跟黑白高爾夫球鞋。<br />\n<br />\n警方公布嫌犯照片後，已經1日下午將他逮捕歸案。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190103/1494357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190103%2F1494357&d=GTD8tfl%2BihbajyS3zzIAv9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2a51b0ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190103%2F1494357&h=442140fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190103/1494357</a>"},{"pid":"a9d0cb8e0e4946a2203bbc70c01f2aa0fd3fe653","tid":967134,"uid":20066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">少</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea35428908374c6d98210fa4a25fa3b8c01c4ad5","tid":967134,"uid":12458,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"咁老你都岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5171ab851922797a43ca7412be30b4e41d70a917","tid":967134,"uid":201768,"like":0,"disli